> ## Welcome to Open Source SAP HANA App Community
***


This community is set up in collaboration with CMU Silicon Valley to showcase the capabilities of HANA Database. Members can create and manage their applications through this community.


_**Please Note**_: Non members have only read access to the community.Please contact cmusvhana@gmail.com for becoming a member of this community and creating a repository.
